## Any other business

There was some discussion about the board election that is coming up in
July. Jonathan suggested that rather than just 2 positions for the
expiring seats we increase the number to 3, to cover the seat lost last
year. There was general agreement about this.

Martin asked if anything had further had been heard from the Jenkins
project, who had been in touch about potentially becoming an associated
project. Nothing had been, so he said he'd get in touch with them to
find out the current status.


